  "text": "The standard industry method of SNR measurement involves taking an FFT of the digitized signal. But it needs a DSP core on chip, which is not always possible by BIST for mixedsignal circuit. We will give another approach -digital narrow band method -proposed in [CITATION_1] . This filter showed in Fig. 3 has two outputs: one is band-pass output tuned to the desired signal frequency; another one is band-stop output including all the harmonic frequency and noise. X in (z) is the filter input, and X bandp (z) is the bandpass output, and X notch (z) is the band-stop output. If we note A 2 (z) as:",
